name: The Tale of Tickle Timothy
description:
Made for Windows 10+

This game was made for Zachbealetv

BEWARE JUMPSCARES ARE PRESENT

This is only my second game so please rate fairly
share if you enjoyed it

You play as Zachariah Beale and your car has crashed. You need to find some help; you discover an old and creepy cabin. You enter and the door locks behind you. You now need to find a way out.
